        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 6 at 10:46PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1046 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Gate, or 13 miles northwest of Laverne, moving southeast at 5 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and pea size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Gate.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
